---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services — Sparkes Mobile Detailing"
  description="Maintenance washes, full details, paint correction, and ceramic coatings. Mobile — we come to you."
>
  <div class="page services">
    <div class="bubble-field" id="services-bubbles"></div>

    <div class="services-head">
      <span class="kicker">Menu · We come to you</span>
      <h1>Our <em>Services.</em></h1>
      <p>
        Professional detailing services tailored to your vehicle's needs. All
        services are mobile — we come to you.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Mobile Detailing -->
    <section class="svc-group">
      <div class="section-h">
        <h2>Mobile Detailing</h2>
        <span class="lead">Wash · Interior · Detail</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tiers">
        <div class="tier">
          <h3 class="tier-name">Basic Wash &amp; Wax</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">Exterior hand wash, dry, and spray wax. Quick and clean.</p>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="from">Starting at</span>
            <span class="amt">$50</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="tier-cta">Book this →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="tier">
          <h3 class="tier-name">Interior Detail</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">Full vacuum, wipe down, leather conditioning, and glass cleaning.</p>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="from">Starting at</span>
            <span class="amt">$75</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="tier-cta">Book this →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="tier feat">
          <span class="tier-flag">Most booked</span>
          <h3 class="tier-name">Full Detail</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">Complete interior and exterior detail. The works.</p>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="from">Starting at</span>
            <span class="amt">$150</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="tier-cta">Book this →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Paint Correction -->
    <section class="svc-group">
      <div class="section-h">
        <h2>Paint Correction</h2>
        <span class="lead">Compound · Polish · Refine</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tiers">
        <div class="tier">
          <h3 class="tier-name">Single Stage Correction</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">Removes light swirl marks and minor imperfections.</p>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="from">Starting at</span>
            <span class="amt">$250</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="tier-cta">Book this →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="tier">
          <h3 class="tier-name">Two Stage Correction</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">Cutting and polishing for moderate scratches and oxidation.</p>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="from">Starting at</span>
            <span class="amt">$400</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="tier-cta">Book this →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="tier">
          <h3 class="tier-name">Multi-Stage Correction</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">Comprehensive correction for heavily damaged paint. Show-car finish.</p>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="from">Starting at</span>
            <span class="amt">$600</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="tier-cta">Book this →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Ceramic Coating -->
    <section class="svc-group">
      <div class="section-h">
        <h2>Ceramic Coating</h2>
        <span class="lead">1 · 3 · 5 year durability</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tiers">
        <div class="tier">
          <h3 class="tier-name">1-Year Coating</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">Entry-level ceramic protection with hydrophobic properties.</p>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="from">Starting at</span>
            <span class="amt">$300</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="tier-cta">Book this →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="tier">
          <h3 class="tier-name">3-Year Coating</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">Professional-grade coating with enhanced durability and gloss.</p>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="from">Starting at</span>
            <span class="amt">$600</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="tier-cta">Book this →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="tier">
          <h3 class="tier-name">5-Year Coating</h3>
          <p class="tier-desc">Premium ceramic coating for maximum protection and shine.</p>
          <div class="tier-price">
            <span class="from">Starting at</span>
            <span class="amt">$1,000</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="tier-cta">Book this →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <p class="svc-disclaimer">Prices may vary based on vehicle size and condition.</p>

    <div class="svc-footer-cta">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get a free quote</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:+18653147405">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="margin-right: 8px; vertical-align: -3px;"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.13.96.36 1.9.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.91.34 1.85.57 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
        Call us · (865) 314-7405
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-wrap">
      <div class="section-h">
        <h2>Frequently asked</h2>
        <span class="lead">Tap to expand</span>
      </div>

      <details class="faq">
        <summary>Where do you actually do the work?</summary>
        <p>In your driveway, garage, or storage facility. We're fully self-contained — water tank and inverter on board — so we don't need a hose bib or a power point.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq">
        <summary>Do prices ever change from what's listed?</summary>
        <p>Prices may vary based on vehicle size and condition. Oversized SUVs, heavily soiled interiors, or paint that needs more than the listed correction tier will get a quote up front — never a surprise on the invoice.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq">
        <summary>How long does a Multi-Stage Correction or 5-Year Coating take?</summary>
        <p>Plan on the car being with us for a day to two days. Correction is paint-condition-dependent, and ceramic coating needs a 12 – 24 hr indoor cure. We can do this in your enclosed garage.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq">
        <summary>How do I book?</summary>
        <p>Call (865) 314-7405, email sparkesautodetailing@gmail.com, or fill in the Get a Quote form. We respond same-day during business hours.</p>
      </details>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-banner">
      <div>
        <h3>Ready when you are.</h3>
        <p>Most new bookings get a slot inside two weeks. Coating slots fill faster — book ahead.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Hey, come wash my car!</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
